<section id="about">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="row text-center">
            <div class="col-lg-12">
                <h2>Keeping Your Employees Fit and Happy</h2>
                <hr class="colored">
            </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-lg-6 col-sm-6">
                <img src="https://cftaskforce.files.wordpress.com/2017/11/tired-at-work.jpg" width="500">
            </div>
            <div class="col-lg-6 col-sm-6">
                <p>
                    Looking for a fun and educational way to jumpstart you and your team's overall health? Look no further than Cigar City CrossFit, located in downtown Ybor.  We offer both nutrition training and group CrossFit classes tailored for business teams.  Our events are a great team building opportunity that are fun, cost effective and empowering.
                </p>

                <p>
                    If you or your team have ever struggled to keep your productivity up after lunch or if you're looking for a team outing that doesn't center around gluttony or alcohol then our on-site nutrition seminar or group training is perfect for you.
                </p>
