                </div>
                <div class="about-content">
                    <p>We come to your office for a 60 minute nutrition seminar that focuses on the fundamentals of fat gain and which foods to eat that promote health and leaness. We offer tips for meal planning, getting through the post lunch slump and improving your mental clarity and productivity.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-6 col-sm-6">
                <div class="text-center">
                <img src="<%= asset_path('dumbbell.svg') %>" style="height:140px" alt="tape measure icon">
                <h3>Group Training Session</h3>
                </div>
                <div class="about-content">
                    <p>Looking for a great team bonding activity? Look no further than a 60 minute group CrossFit class exclusively for your business.  It's beginner focused and prioritizes safety and technique first.  Led by an experienced CrossFit coach, you and your team will sweat together while laughing and cheering each other on.</p>
                </div>
